## Educational Use Note

This repository contains my personal solutions to the Johns Hopkins University 
Data Science Specialization assignments on Coursera.

The code is shared for educational and reference purposes. If you are taking 
the same course, I encourage you to:

1. Try to solve the assignments on your own first
2. Use this code only as a reference or for comparison
3. Respect your course's academic honesty policies

Learning happens best when you personally tackle problem-solving!
